  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - "Ah, you're awake. Ready to begin your training? \n\n\nPress [E] to continue"
  - Today your journey into alchemy starts. Stay close to me, and one day you may
    stand where I stand.
  - Alchemy forbids human transmutation, sadly, so you'll stay exactly that height.
    But your name, that we can make grow.
  - Alchemy is the art of fusing elements into new ones. We create nothing from nothing;
    we only transmute what we have into what we want.
  - So first you must gather the four core elements every lab needs.
  - We begin with water. Walk to the river, and press [E] to interact with the world
    around you.
